msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The Bayesian A/B test allows one to monitor the evidence for the hypotheses "
"that an intervention or treatment has either a positive effect, a negative "
"effect or no effect."
msgstr ""
"貝氏A/B檢定可用於監測支持某介入或處理具有正向效果、負向效果或無任何效果之假設"
"的證據。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"**Input**\n"
"1. Each of the below elements needs to be an integer.\n"
"2. A cumulative sequence of successes/trials can also be given as input."
msgstr ""
"**輸入**\n"
"1.以下各項元素皆須為整數。\n"
"2.亦可輸入成功次數／試驗次數之累積序列。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Number of successes in group 1 (control condition)."
msgstr "第 1 組（對照條件）的成功次數。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Number of trials in group 1 (control condition)."
msgstr "第 1 組（對照條件）的試驗次數。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Number of successes in group 2 (experimental condition)."
msgstr "第 2 組（實驗條件）的成功次數。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Number of trials in group 2 (experimental condition)."
msgstr "第 2 組（實驗條件）的試驗次數。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Specifies the mean for the normal prior on the test-relevant log odds ratio."
msgstr "指定檢定相關之對數勝算比其常態先驗分配的平均數。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Specifies the standard deviation for the normal prior on the test-relevant "
"log odds ratio."
msgstr "指定檢定相關之對數勝算比其常態先驗分配的標準差。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the counts and proportion for each group."
msgstr "顯示各組的次數與比例。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the prior and posterior density for the quantity of interest."
msgstr "顯示關注量數的先驗與後驗密度。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the development of posterior probabilities as the data come in. The "
"probability wheels visualize prior and posterior probabilities of the "
"hypotheses."
msgstr ""
"顯示隨著資料陸續納入，後驗機率的發展變化。機率圓餅圖可視化呈現各假設的先驗與"
"後驗機率。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Plots parameter prior distributions."
msgstr "繪製參數的先驗分配圖。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the prior sensitivity analysis."
msgstr "顯示先驗敏感度分析。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Compares each model against the model selected"
msgstr "將每個模型與所選定的模型進行比較"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Compare to best model."
msgstr "與最佳模型進行比較。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Compare to null model."
msgstr "與虛無模型進行比較。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Specifies the prior probabilities for the four hypotheses."
msgstr "指定四個假設的先驗機率。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Specifies that the 'success' probability is identical (there is no effect)."
msgstr "指定「成功」機率為相等（無任何效果）。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Specifies that the 'success' probability in the experimental condition is "
"higher than in the control condition."
msgstr "指定實驗條件下的「成功」機率高於對照條件。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Specifies that the 'success' probability in the experimental condition is "
"lower than in the control condition."
msgstr "指定實驗條件下的「成功」機率低於對照條件。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Specifies that the 'success' probability differs between the control and "
"experimental condition, but does not specify which one is higher."
msgstr "指定對照條件與實驗條件之間的「成功」機率有差異，但未指明何者較高。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of importance samples for obtaining log marginal "
"likelihood for (H+) and (H-) and the number of posterior samples."
msgstr ""
"指定用於取得 (H+) 與 (H-) 對數邊際概似度之重要性樣本數，以及後驗樣本數。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Specifies in how many discrete steps the μ step range is partitioned."
msgstr "指定將 μ 步階範圍劃分為多少個離散步階。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Specifies in how many discrete steps the σ step range is partitioned."
msgstr "指定將 σ 步階範圍劃分為多少個離散步階。"

msgctxt "ABTestBayesian|"
msgid "Specifies the range of μ and σ values to consider."
msgstr "指定要考慮的 μ 與 σ 值範圍。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"The binomial test allows the user to test whether a proportion of a "
"dichotomous variable is equal to a test value (=presumed population value). "
"The analysis returns a binomial test for each level of the dependent "
"variable against all other levels, so it will also work for variables with "
"more than two levels.\n"
"## Assumptions\n"
"- The variable should be a dichotomous scale.\n"
"- Observations should be independent."
msgstr ""
"二項檢定允許使用者檢驗二元變項的比例是否等於指定的檢定值（即假定的母體值）。"
"分析會針對依變項的每個層級與其他所有層級進行二項檢定，因此也適用於層級超過兩"
"個的變項。\n"
"## 假設條件\n"
"- 變項應為二元尺度。\n"
"- 觀察值應彼此獨立。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"The proportion of the variable under the null hypothesis - the baseline for "
"comparison."
msgstr "虛無假設下該變項的比例 — 即比較的基準。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Two-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion is not equal to test "
"value."
msgstr "雙尾對立假設，即比例不等於檢定值。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion is larger than the test "
"value."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即比例大於檢定值。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion is smaller than the "
"test value."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即比例小於檢定值。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Coverage of the confidence intervals in percentages. The default value is 95."
msgstr "信賴區間的涵蓋率（以百分比表示）。預設值為 95。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"An upper bound on how much more likely a p-value is under the alternative "
"hypothesis than under the null."
msgstr "在對立假設下比在虛無假設下，p 值更可能出現的上限倍數。"

msgctxt "BinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Visualises the proportion and confidence interval of the two different "
"values of your dichotomous variable."
msgstr "視覺化呈現二元變項中兩個不同數值的比例及其信賴區間。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The Bayesian binomial test allows you to test whether a proportion of a "
"dichotomous variable is equal to a test value (presumed population value). "
"The analysis returns a binomial test for each level of the dependent "
"variable against all other levels, so it will also work for variables with "
"more than two levels.\n"
"## Assumptions\n"
"- The variable should be a dichotomous scale.\n"
"- Observations should be independent."
msgstr ""
"貝氏二項式檢定讓您得以檢定二元變項的比例是否等於某檢定值（即假設的母群體"
"值）。該分析會針對依變項的每個水準與其他所有水準進行二項式檢定，因此也適用於"
"超過兩個水準的變項。\n"
"## 假定\n"
"- 變項應為二元尺度。\n"
"- 觀察值應具有獨立性。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The proportion of the variable under the null hypothesis - the baseline for "
"comparison."
msgstr "虛無假設下該變項的比例 — 即比較的基準。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Two-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion is not equal to test "
"value."
msgstr "雙尾對立假設，即比例不等於檢定值。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion is larger than the test "
"value."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即比例大於檢定值。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion is smaller than the "
"test value."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即比例小於檢定值。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Sets how much prior belief you have in success. When a = b = 1, this "
"corresponds to a uniform prior distribution."
msgstr ""
"設定您對成功所持有的先驗信念程度。當 a = b = 1 時，此對應於均勻先驗分配。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Sets how much prior belief you have in failure. When a = b = 1, this "
"corresponds to a uniform prior distribution."
msgstr ""
"設定您對失敗所持有的先驗信念程度。當 a = b = 1 時，此對應於均勻先驗分配。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the prior and posterior density of the population proportion under "
"the alternative hypothesis."
msgstr "顯示對立假設下母群體比例的先驗與後驗密度。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Shows the Bayes factor using the chosen prior, a probability wheel showing "
"evidence for each hypothesis, and the median with 95% credible interval of "
"the effect size."
msgstr ""
"顯示使用所選先驗之貝氏因子、呈現各假設證據強度的機率圓餅圖，以及效果量的中位"
"數與 95% 可信區間。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the development of the Bayes factor as the data come in using the "
"user-defined prior."
msgstr "顯示在使用者定義的先驗下，隨著資料陸續納入，貝氏因子的發展變化。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Display descriptives plots."
msgstr "顯示描述性統計圖。"

msgctxt "BinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Display central credible intervals. A credible interval shows the "
"probability that the true effect size lies within certain values. The "
"default credible interval is set at 95%."
msgstr ""
"顯示中心可信區間。可信區間表示真實效果量落在特定數值範圍內的機率。預設可信區"
"間設為 95%。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Contingency tables allow the user to identify how the frequencies of one "
"categorical variable relate to another, helping to determine associations "
"between variables."
msgstr ""
"列聯表讓使用者得以識別一個類別變項的次數如何與另一個類別變項相關，有助於判定"
"變項之間的關聯性。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Pearson’s chi-squared test for independence."
msgstr "皮爾森獨立性卡方檢定。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Applies Yates’ correction for continuity (for 2×2 tables)."
msgstr "套用葉氏連續性校正（適用於 2×2 表格）。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Calculates the likelihood of the data under the alternative hypothesis "
"divided by the likelihood of the data under the null hypothesis."
msgstr "計算對立假設下資料的概似度除以虛無假設下資料的概似度。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"An upper bound on how much more likely a p-value is under the alternative "
"hypothesis than under the null."
msgstr "在對立假設下比在虛無假設下，p 值更可能出現的上限倍數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Displays the odds ratio for 2×2 tables (ad/bc)."
msgstr "顯示 2×2 表格的勝算比 (ad/bc)。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Shows the log-transformed odds ratio."
msgstr "顯示取對數轉換後的勝算比。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Coverage of the confidence intervals in percentages. The default value is 95."
msgstr "信賴區間的涵蓋率（以百分比表示）。預設值為 95。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Specify the direction of the alternative hypothesis for Fisher's exact test."
msgstr "指定費雪精確檢定之對立假設的方向。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Two-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion of group 1 is not equal "
"to the proportion of group 2."
msgstr "雙尾對立假設，即第一組之比例不等於第二組之比例。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion of group 1 is greater "
"than the proportion of group 2."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即第一組之比例大於第二組之比例。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion of group 1 is less than "
"the proportion of group 2."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即第一組之比例小於第二組之比例。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Measure of association for nominal variables (based on χ²)."
msgstr "名義變項的關聯量數（基於 χ²）。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Effect size for nominal association; Phi (2×2), Cramer’s V (larger tables)."
msgstr ""
"名義關聯的效果量：Phi（適用於 2×2 表格）、Cramer’s V（適用於較大表格）。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Proportion reduction in error measure for nominal data."
msgstr "名義資料的誤差比例降低量數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Measure of ordinal association based on concordant/discordant pairs."
msgstr "基於一致對／不一致對的順序關聯量數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Ordinal correlation adjusting for ties."
msgstr "調整同分序位後的順序相關。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Show actual counts from the data."
msgstr "顯示資料中的實際次數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Show counts expected under the null hypothesis."
msgstr "顯示虛無假設下的期望次數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Computed by (observed - expected)."
msgstr "計算方式為（觀察次數 - 期望次數）。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Standardized residuals; computed by (observed - expected) / √(expected)."
msgstr "標準化殘差；計算方式為 (觀察值 − 期望值) ÷ √(期望值)。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Adjusted Pearson"
msgstr "調整皮爾森"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Accounts for row/column totals; computed by (observed - expected) / "
"√(expected × (1 - row marginal proportion) × (1 - column marginal "
"proportion))."
msgstr ""
"考慮行/列總計；計算方式為 (觀察值 − 期望值) ÷ √(期望值 × (1 − 行邊際比例) × "
"(1 − 列邊際比例))。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Shows row-wise percentages."
msgstr "顯示列百分比。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Shows column-wise percentages."
msgstr "顯示行百分比。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Shows percentages of total."
msgstr "顯示總計百分比。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Shows row and column totals."
msgstr "顯示列總計與行總計。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Rows sorted in numerical order."
msgstr "列按數值順序排序。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Rows sorted in reverse numerical order."
msgstr "列按數值反向順序排序。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Columns sorted in numerical order."
msgstr "行按數值順序排序。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Columns sorted in reverse numerical order."
msgstr "行按數值反向順序排序。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Assumes independent Poisson-distributed counts for each cell."
msgstr "假設每個細格的次數為獨立卜瓦松分佈。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Assumes all cell counts come from one multinomial distribution."
msgstr "假設所有細格次數來自同一多項式分配。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Each row is a separate multinomial distribution; row totals are fixed."
msgstr "每一列為獨立的多項式分配；列總計為固定。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Each column is a separate multinomial distribution; column totals are fixed."
msgstr "每一行為獨立的多項式分配；行總計為固定。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Assumes fixed row and column totals; suitable for exact tests."
msgstr "假設列總計與行總計皆為固定；適用於精確檢定。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the odds ratio for 2×2 tables (ad/bc) with a credible interval."
msgstr "顯示 2×2 表格的勝算比 (ad/bc) 及其可信區間。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Range where the true log odds ratio likely falls, given the data."
msgstr "在給定資料下，真實對數勝算比可能落入的範圍。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Two-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion of group 1 is not equal "
"to the proportion of group 2."
msgstr "雙尾對立假設，即第一組之比例不等於第二組之比例。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion of group 1 is greater "
"than the proportion of group 2."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即第一組之比例大於第二組之比例。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid ""
"One-sided alternative hypothesis that the proportion of group 1 is less than "
"the proportion of group 2."
msgstr "單尾對立假設，即第一組之比例小於第二組之比例。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Displays a graphical summary of the log odds ratio."
msgstr "顯示對數勝算比之圖形化摘要。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Controls how strongly the prior favours equal proportions."
msgstr "控制先驗在多大程度上傾向於支持比例相等。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Show actual counts from the data."
msgstr "顯示資料中的實際次數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Show counts expected under the null hypothesis."
msgstr "顯示虛無假設下的期望次數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Shows row-wise percentages."
msgstr "顯示列百分比。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Shows column-wise percentages."
msgstr "顯示行百分比。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Shows percentages of total."
msgstr "顯示總計百分比。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Shows row and column totals."
msgstr "顯示列總計與行總計。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Rows sorted in numerical order."
msgstr "列按數值順序排序。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Rows sorted in reverse numerical order."
msgstr "列按數值反向順序排序。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Columns sorted in numerical order."
msgstr "行按數值順序排序。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTablesBayesian|"
msgid "Columns sorted in reverse numerical order."
msgstr "行按數值反向順序排序。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Compares each model to an encompassing (broad) model that includes all "
"others."
msgstr "將每個模型與一個涵蓋（廣泛）模型進行比較，該模型包含了所有其他模型。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Compares each model to the null (equal proportions)."
msgstr "將每個模型與虛無模型（比例相等）進行比較。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Compares each model against a specific selected model."
msgstr "將每個模型與某個特定選定的模型進行比較。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays a summary table of observed counts or proportions."
msgstr "顯示觀察次數或比例之摘要表格。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Shows a plot of observed counts or proportions."
msgstr "顯示觀察次數或比例的圖形。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as counts."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以次數呈現。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as a proportion."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以比例呈現。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the posterior distribution with credible intervals."
msgstr "顯示具有可信區間的後驗分配。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the development of the Bayes factor or posterior probability as the "
"data come in."
msgstr "顯示隨著資料陸續納入，貝氏因子或後驗機率的發展變化。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the progression of Bayes factor values."
msgstr "顯示貝氏因子數值的進展。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the progression of the posterior probability."
msgstr "顯示後驗機率的進展。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Number of initial MCMC samples to discard before analysis begins, allowing "
"the chain to stabilize."
msgstr "在分析開始前，預先捨棄的初始 MCMC 樣本數，以使馬可夫鏈達到穩定。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Total number of MCMC samples used for estimating the posterior after burn-in."
msgstr "預燃期後用於估計後驗的 MCMC 樣本總數。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Max number of samples used to estimate marginal likelihoods for computing "
"Bayes factors."
msgstr "用於估計邊際概似度以計算貝氏因子的最大樣本數。"

msgctxt "InformedBinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Number of data points at which the Bayes factor is updated during sequential "
"analysis."
msgstr "在序列分析期間，更新貝氏因子的資料點數。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Compares each model to the null (equal proportions)."
msgstr "將每個模型與虛無模型（比例相等）進行比較。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Compares each model to an encompassing (broad) model that includes all "
"others."
msgstr "將每個模型與一個涵蓋（廣泛）模型進行比較，該模型包含了所有其他模型。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Compares each model against a specific selected model."
msgstr "將每個模型與某個特定選定的模型進行比較。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays a summary table of observed counts or proportions."
msgstr "顯示觀察次數或比例之摘要表格。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Shows a plot of observed counts or proportions."
msgstr "顯示觀察次數或比例的圖形。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as counts."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以次數呈現。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as a proportion."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以比例呈現。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the posterior distribution with credible intervals."
msgstr "顯示具有可信區間的後驗分配。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the development of the Bayes factor or posterior probability as the "
"data come in."
msgstr "顯示隨著資料陸續納入，貝氏因子或後驗機率的發展變化。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the progression of Bayes factor values."
msgstr "顯示貝氏因子數值的進展。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the progression of the posterior probability."
msgstr "顯示後驗機率的進展。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Number of initial MCMC samples to discard before analysis begins, allowing "
"the chain to stabilize."
msgstr "在分析開始前，預先捨棄的初始 MCMC 樣本數，以使馬可夫鏈達到穩定。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Total number of MCMC samples used for estimating the posterior after burn-in."
msgstr "預燃期後用於估計後驗的 MCMC 樣本總數。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Max number of samples used to estimate marginal likelihoods for computing "
"Bayes factors."
msgstr "用於估計邊際概似度以計算貝氏因子的最大樣本數。"

msgctxt "InformedMultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Number of data points at which the Bayes factor is updated during sequential "
"analysis."
msgstr "在序列分析期間，更新貝氏因子的資料點數。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"The multinomial test allows the user to test whether an observed "
"distribution of cell counts corresponds to an expected distribution.\n"
"## Assumptions\n"
"- The variable of interest should be categorical."
msgstr ""
"多項式檢定讓使用者得以檢定觀察到的細格次數分配是否符合某期望分配。\n"
"## 假定\n"
"- 關注的變項應為類別變項。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid "**Input**"
msgstr "**輸入**"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid "The categorical variable we are interested in."
msgstr "我們關注的類別變項。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid "The variable that contains the count data."
msgstr "包含次數資料的變項。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"If the data includes a variable representing expected cell counts, enter it "
"here; its values define the null hypothesis."
msgstr "若資料包含代表期望細格次數的變項，請在此輸入；其數值將定義虛無假設。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Checks if observed counts across categories are uniformly distributed. It "
"compares observed counts to what we'd expect by chance using a chi-squared "
"test. A significant difference suggests the categories aren't equally likely."
msgstr ""
"檢查各類別的觀察次數是否為均勻分配。它使用卡方檢定將觀察次數與隨機期望下的次"
"數進行比較。若差異顯著，則表示各類別並非具有相同機率。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Checks if observed counts match a specific expected distribution. By "
"default, it tests for a uniform distribution, but you can set your own "
"expectations. A significant difference suggests the actual distribution "
"doesn’t fit the expected one."
msgstr ""
"檢查觀察次數是否符合某個特定的期望分配。預設情況下，它檢定是否為均勻分配，但"
"您也可以設定自己的期望值。若差異顯著，則表示實際分配不符合期望分配。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Displays the descriptives of the observed and expected counts as well as the "
"confidence intervals of the observed values."
msgstr "顯示觀察次數與期望次數的描述性統計，以及觀察值的信賴區間。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Coverage of the confidence intervals in percentages. The default value is 95."
msgstr "信賴區間的涵蓋率（以百分比表示）。預設值為 95。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"An upper bound on how much more likely a p-value is under the alternative "
"hypothesis than under the null."
msgstr "在對立假設下比在虛無假設下，p 值更可能出現的上限倍數。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as counts."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以次數呈現。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as a proportion."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以比例呈現。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTest|"
msgid ""
"Plots the frequencies and the confidence intervals of the observed counts."
msgstr "繪製觀察次數的次數及其信賴區間圖。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"The Bayesian multinomial test allows the user to test whether an observed "
"distribution of cell counts corresponds to an expected distribution.\n"
"## Assumptions\n"
"- The variable of interest should be categorical."
msgstr ""
"貝氏多項式檢定讓使用者得以檢定觀察到的細格次數分配是否符合某期望分配。\n"
"## 假定\n"
"- 關注的變項應為類別變項。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "**Input**"
msgstr "**輸入**"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "The categorical variable we are interested in."
msgstr "我們關注的類別變項。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "The variable that contains the count data."
msgstr "包含次數資料的變項。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"If the data includes a variable representing expected cell counts, enter it "
"here; its values define the null hypothesis."
msgstr "若資料包含代表期望細格次數的變項，請在此輸入；其數值將定義虛無假設。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Checks if observed counts across categories are uniformly distributed (the "
"null hypothesis). A significant difference suggests the categories aren't "
"equally likely."
msgstr ""
"檢查各類別的觀察次數是否為均勻分配（虛無假設）。若差異顯著，則表示各類別並非"
"具有相同機率。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Checks if observed counts match a specific expected distribution (the null "
"hypothesis). By default, it tests for a uniform distribution, but you can "
"set your own expectations. A significant difference suggests the actual "
"distribution doesn’t fit the expected one."
msgstr ""
"檢查觀察次數是否符合某個特定的期望分配（虛無假設）。預設情況下，它檢定是否為"
"均勻分配，但您也可以設定自己的期望值。若差異顯著，則表示實際分配不符合期望分"
"配。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays a table containing the categories of interest, the observed values "
"and the expected values under the specified hypotheses."
msgstr "顯示包含關注類別、觀察值及指定假設下的期望值的表格。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Display central credible intervals. A credible interval shows the "
"probability that the true effect size lies within certain values. The "
"default credible interval is set at 95%."
msgstr ""
"顯示中心可信區間。可信區間表示真實效果量落在特定數值範圍內的機率。預設可信區"
"間設為 95%。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as counts."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以次數呈現。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid "Displays the descriptives as a proportion."
msgstr "將描述性統計結果以比例呈現。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Displays the frequency of the reported counts and the corresponding credible "
"intervals for every level of the variable of interest."
msgstr "顯示所報告次數的頻率，以及關注變項每個水層對應的可信區間。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"A credible interval shows the probability that the true effect size lies "
"within certain values. The default credible interval is set at 95%."
msgstr "可信區間表示真實效果量落在特定數值範圍內的機率。預設可信區間設為 95%。"

msgctxt "MultinomialTestBayesian|"
msgid ""
"Option to adjust the prior distribution for the vector of cell probabilities."
msgstr "調整細格機率向量之先驗分配的選項。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinear|"
msgid ""
"Log-linear regression models the logarithm of the dependent variable as a "
"linear combination of independent variables. It is useful for handling "
"skewed data and multiplicative relationships."
msgstr ""
"對數線性迴歸將依變項的對數，建模為自變項的線性組合。此方法適用於處理偏態資料"
"與乘法關係。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinear|"
msgid ""
"Displays estimates of the regression coefficients along with their standard "
"errors, Z-values, and associated p-values."
msgstr "顯示迴歸係數的估計值，連同其標準誤、Z值及對應的p值。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinear|"
msgid ""
"Coverage of the confidence intervals in percentages. The default value is 95."
msgstr "信賴區間的涵蓋率（以百分比表示）。預設值為 95。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinear|"
msgid ""
"An upper bound on how much more likely a p-value is under the alternative "
"hypothesis than under the null."
msgstr "在對立假設下比在虛無假設下，p 值更可能出現的上限倍數。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Specifies the shape of the prior distribution on the effect size."
msgstr "指定效果量之先驗分配的形狀。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Controls how spread out the prior is; larger = more uncertainty."
msgstr "控制先驗分配的離散程度；數值越大表示不確定性越高。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Shows the top N models ranked by posterior probability."
msgstr "顯示按後驗機率排序的前 N 個模型。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Only models with posterior probability above this threshold are shown."
msgstr "僅顯示後驗機率高於此閾值的模型。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Displays estimated regression coefficients for included terms."
msgstr "顯示納入項目的迴歸係數估計值。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Adds a credible interval for each coefficient estimate."
msgstr "為每個係數估計值添加可信區間。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Displays statistics for a specific model index."
msgstr "顯示特定模型索引的統計量。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Shows credible intervals for the selected submodel's coefficients."
msgstr "顯示所選子模型係數的可信區間。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Automatically chooses the number of samples for estimation."
msgstr "自動選擇估計所需的樣本數。"

msgctxt "RegressionLogLinearBayesian|"
msgid "Allows you to set the number of posterior samples manually."
msgstr "允許您手動設定後驗樣本數。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "McNemar's χ² test"
msgstr "McNemar χ² 檢定"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "Tests equality of two marginal proportions in paired nominal data."
msgstr "檢定配對名義資料中兩個邊際比例是否相等。"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid "McNemar's χ² continuity correction"
msgstr "McNemar χ² 檢定的連續性修正"

msgctxt "ContingencyTables|"
msgid ""
"Corrects for error introduced when approximating a discrete distribution "
"with a continuous one in McNemar's test."
msgstr "修正以連續分配近似離散分配時，在 McNemar 檢定中所產生的誤差。"
